# ============================================================================
#
# UPSTREAM
#   Repository : https://github.com/btcsuite/btcwallet
#   Maintainer : btcsuite developers (the original developers of
#                btcd ‚Äî a from-scratch Go reimplementation of the
#                Bitcoin Core protocol; the upstream Lightning
